      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "Card proposes evaluating GAT and MPNN architectures; paper only evaluates GraphCCS, SigmaCCS, and Mol2CCS (an extension of SigmaCCS with additional features, not a different GNN architecture type).",
        "Card frames task as 'substituting an alternative GNN architecture'; paper's Mol2CCS is not a substitution of the GNN core but an augmentation with additional feature modules alongside the same ECC-based GNN.",
