      "asbval:note": "Paper does not employ ablation studies or gradient-based saliency scoring. The paper does extend SigmaCCS with additional features (Morgan fingerprints, molecular descriptors, instrument type, molecule type) but this is feature engineering for model improvement, not post-hoc attribution analysis.",
