      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "In the first setting, we trained each model on 80% of one database (METLIN-CCS or CCSBase) and tested it on the remaining 20% of the same database. This method evaluated the model's ability to predict CCS values for chemicals within a similar chemical space.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper distinguishes between same-database evaluation (similar chemical space) and cross-database evaluation (novel chemical space).",
