      "asbval:note": "The paper does not mention or reference an 'enveda/ccs-prediction' repository. The paper benchmarks published models (GraphCCS, SigmaCCS) and develops Mol2CCS as an extension of SigmaCCS, but does not cite a specific GitHub repository as a source of pre-trained weights or utilities.",
