    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/gnn-model-inference-and-prediction/004",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "We evaluated the performance of the two most accurate ML models trained to predict CCS values: GraphCCS [22], and SigmaCCS [6]. We retrained these models using the reported hyperparameters on the datasets used in this work... Since Mol2CCS is an extension of SigmaCCS [6], we expanded upon its codebase for its implementation.",
