      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Select and implement alternative message-passing graph neural network architectures (e.g., Graph Attention Networks, Message-Passing Neural Networks) as drop-in replacements for a baseline GNN model, maintaining input/output dimensionality and training protocol to enable direct p",
