      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "First, we divided the entire dataset (CCSBase and METLIN-CCS data combined) into five distinct groups: lipids, dimers carbohydrates, peptides, and everything else. This categorization ensured that each of these categories was represented in the train and test sets.",
