      "asbval:note": "RDKit is used in the paper for SMILES parsing and molecular graph construction, but NOT for the claimed purpose of feature ablation or saliency mapping. The paper uses RDKit for feature extraction (Morgan fingerprints, molecular descriptors) but does not perform post-hoc interpretability analysis.",
