    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/regression-metric-computation-rmse-mae-r2/005",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "We benchmarked all the models using three different settings. In the first setting, we trained each model on 80% of one database (METLIN-CCS or CCSBase) and tested it on the remaining 20% of the same database. This method evaluated the model's ability to predict CCS values for chemicals within a similar chemical space.",
